subSubSection.paragraph:
Antennule (Fig. 
3A
). Eleven-segmented, not reaching posterior margin of cephalothorax, ornamented with refractile points. Armature formula as follows: 6.2.5.2.0.2.3.1+A.2.2.6+A; all setae smooth; aesthetascs slender, fused basally with seta as acrotheck.

